{"tid":2342822,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★學者呼籲禁止 Tesla 自動駕駛功能　批評為收集數據犧牲公衆安全","createTime":"2020-12-27T12:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T08:15:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"892bc4de489a85ffc648ee4600db0d52fad0ea23","tid":2342822,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"Tesla 的自動駕駛系統是他們重點開發的技術之一，而在其開發過程之中，都會有測試階段，讓部分車主率先試用功能並收集數據。有學者就擔心此舉是漠視公衆安全，要求政府禁止此類測試。<br />\n<br />\nTesla 的 Full Self Driving (FSD) 功能暫時仍然在 beta 測試階段，但已經向部分車主提供試用。哈佛大學甘迺迪政府學院的學者 David Zipper 最近就表示，拜登團隊上任總統之後，必須向 Tesla 大刀闊斧禁止其公衆試驗行爲，他認爲 Tesla 將未完成的試驗中功能提供及車主在公共道路使用是非常危險。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Zipper 認爲 Autopilot 和 FSD 都不是真正的自動駕駛，仍然需要車主的介入，而 Tesla 對這些功能的處理態度不當，在汽車產業開了危險的先例。美國國家道路安全管理局 (NHTSA) 必須更積極管理並阻止 Tesla 的行為，不然其他車廠將會跟隨 Tesla 犧牲公共安全繞過監管機構的限制來開發其自動駕駛技術。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/27/tesla-biden-self-driving-cars-regulation/life-tech/auto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F27%2Ftesla-biden-self-driving-cars-regulation%2Flife-tech%2Fauto%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=bb745ffc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/27/tesla-biden-self-driving-cars-regulation/life-tech/auto/</a>"},{"pid":"9f9eac08987004d1e6bc382f3152d1c12afff568","tid":2342822,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1r2otFE.gif&amp;h=d874001e&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"1848d632f0af12f3bbcfe3dd466b5cab870f54cf","tid":2342822,"uid":308251,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"又唔見佢屌中國疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacad7def710d2ecf828fd4d8f9e8ae12d32646b","tid":2342822,"uid":68220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"又阻止科技進步"},{"pid":"a8bc30631589bc37618cfc307d9c422c15ee445f","tid":2342822,"uid":18948,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"唔俾試用，唔會100%安全<br />\n<br />\n唔 100% 安全，唔俾試用"},{"pid":"bff40d1a585807119db0cf36749f5c7568501749","tid":2342822,"uid":168366,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:20:52.000Z","msg":"不如比較下有周無的意外率先9up la<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉無人駕駛汽車司機因「超速時打瞌睡」被控<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-54201767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-54201767&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=2ffdef3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-54201767&h=391a652a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-54201767</a><br />\n<br />\n一名特斯拉（Tesla）男性駕駛員最近在加拿大被控危險駕駛。據稱他在車輛行駛過程中打瞌睡，當時他的特斯拉自動駕駛汽車時速超過150公里/小時。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大阿爾伯塔省（Alberta）警方稱，他們接到事件報告後發現，事發車輛的兩張前排座椅均被完全放平，駕駛員與乘客明顯已經睡著。<br />\n<br />\n這輛車型號為特斯拉Model S，事發時駕駛速度為140公里/小時，而在一名警員亮起緊急警報燈後，車輛提速至150公里/小時。"},{"pid":"607c0eddbae7fff8be567fab89234bfbab748ac9","tid":2342822,"uid":250055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"用馬車啦屌你"},{"pid":"90b97476a47d77252391e119904f33ab5aa138f4","tid":2342822,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"美國石丹理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add2ec55da7593f3039ef1ea79ae1c1ce6168b46","tid":2342822,"uid":101328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8bc30631589bc37618cfc307d9c422c15ee445f","tid":2342822,"uid":18948,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"唔俾試用，唔會100%安全<br />\n<br />\n唔 100% 安全，唔俾試用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T20:38:52.000Z","msg":"請新人，但要有3年工作經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6604b0749c7de9a28d067